# Shared utilities (`shared/utils/`)

## Date input (`date-input.ts`)

Used by `FormTextFieldComponent` (native date `min`/`max`), `DatePeriodPickerComponent`, and table date-range filters.

| Export | Role |
|--------|------|
| `DatePeriodValue` | `{ from?: string; to?: string }` — shared value shape for picker + filters |
| `todayIsoDate()` | Current local date as `YYYY-MM-DD` |
| `resolveDateInputBound(value)` | Resolves `'today'` → today ISO; passes through ISO strings |
| `resolveFieldDateBound(bound, formValue)` | Resolves `FieldDef.minDate` / `maxDate` (static or `(value) => …`) |
| `notPastDateValidator()` | `FormGroup` validator — value must be ≥ today (`minDate` error) |
| `endDateOnOrAfterStartValidator(startKey)` | End date ≥ today **and** ≥ start field (`minDate` / `dateRange` errors) |
| `buildCalendarMonth(year, month)` | Monday-start grid of `CalendarCell` for picker UI |
| `isDatePeriodDisabled(iso, context)` | Disables past dates (`minDate`) and dates before start while picking end |
| `sanitizeDatePeriodValue(value, options?)` | Cleans partial ranges; optional `minDate`, `allowPartial` |
| `initialCalendarMonth(value, minDate?)` | Opens picker on month of existing selection or today |
| `isoDateFromLocal(year, month, day)` | Builds `YYYY-MM-DD` for calendar cells |

### Form field defs (`FieldDef`)

```typescript
minDate: 'today',
maxDate: (value) => value.transportStartDate || 'today',
```

Types: `DateInputBoundValue = string | 'today'`; bound can be static or `(formValue) => …`.

### Form page validators

Mirror def constraints on the `FormGroup` — validators live on the page, not only in `FieldDef`:

```typescript
import { endDateOnOrAfterStartValidator, notPastDateValidator } from '…/shared/utils/date-input';

transportStartDate: ['', [Validators.required, notPastDateValidator()]],
transportEndDate: ['', [Validators.required, endDateOnOrAfterStartValidator('transportStartDate')]],
```

When start date changes, re-validate end date:

```typescript
this.form.get('transportStartDate')?.valueChanges
  .pipe(takeUntilDestroyed(this.destroyRef))
  .subscribe(() => this.form.get('transportEndDate')?.updateValueAndValidity({ emitEvent: false }));
```

**Reference:** `portal/user/features/transport/form/transport-form-page.component.ts`, `portal/user/features/freight/form/freight-form-page.component.ts`, `portal/user/features/warehouse/form/warehouse-form-page.component.ts`.

### Error i18n

`shared.form.common.errors.minDate`, `shared.form.common.errors.dateRange` — registered in `form-control-error.ts` (`DEFAULT_ERROR_PRIORITY` / `DEFAULT_ERROR_KEYS`).

### Date period picker UX (implemented in `DatePeriodPickerComponent`)

- **Range flow:** first click sets start; second click ≥ start sets end and closes panel (forms/filters).
- **Hover preview:** before start — hovered day shows full selected pill; after start — hovered end day shows selected end-cap, days between show in-range band. Generic day `:hover` must not override preview/selected classes.
- **Clear dates** in panel: clears value, **keeps panel open** (no hint text row).
- **Single mode:** `periodMode: 'single'` / filter `singleDate: true` — one click selects and closes.

Picker i18n: `shared.datePeriod.*` — see `i18n.mdc`, `layout.mdc`.

## Display date formatting (`format-display-date.ts`)

| Export | Role |
|--------|------|
| `formatDisplayDate(value)` | Formats ISO/date values as `Jul 3, 2026` — used by `DataTableComponent`, `DateRangeDisplayComponent`, `DatePeriodPickerComponent`, and detail pages |

Do not duplicate date formatting in feature code — import `formatDisplayDate` from `shared/utils/format-display-date.ts`.

## Search normalization (`normalize-for-search.ts`)

| Export | Role |
|--------|------|
| `normalizeForSearch(value)` | Lowercase, trim, strip BiH diacritics (č→c, š→s, …), NFD + remove combining marks |

Used by `FormAutocompleteFieldComponent` to filter options. Reuse for table search / filters when matching user-typed text against BiH place names.

Related: `forms.mdc`, `shared-constants.mdc` (`BIH_CITY_OPTIONS`)
